{"tid":1593694,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［一齊裝］有線新聞推出新手機程式   提供 HDR 畫質 24 小時新聞直播","createTime":"2019-09-25T07:51:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T10:48:38.000Z","uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9500aa64dd3ed9028bc44c59700e81563ac13969","tid":1593694,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"現時很多人都透過智能電話接收新聞資訊，有線寬頻旗下的有線電視亦積極配合市民的習慣轉變，日前宣佈推出全港首個採用 HDR 制式的 24 小時 OTT（over-the-top）直播新聞手機程式「有線新聞 OTT App」，iOS 和 Android 版本已經上架。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/25/141324_92b09e623e988a77340662f23059ac9f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F25%2F141324_92b09e623e988a77340662f23059ac9f.jpeg&h=ba22bf60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線新聞 OTT App 提供新聞和財經資訊之餘，亦提供一系列有線新聞製作的節目，還有 24 消息新聞直播，不過此 App 的賣點之一，相信是畫質更佳，更能夠符合用戶要求的 HDR 制式。有線新聞 OTT App 現在屬於試用階段，用戶登記成為會員，可以由即日起至今年 12 月 31 日免費觀看本地、大陸、國際的新聞時事、財經及體育資訊。<br />\n<br />\n正式推出日期預計為明年年初，然後會進一步推出智能電視版本，讓用戶透過手機和智能電視跨平台收看有線新聞直播或點播內容。<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞<br />\n下載：iOS<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/id1433886832\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B7%259A%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2Fid1433886832&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9A1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=233e6787\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/id1433886832</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.hkott.app\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dhk.hkott.app&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9A1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=cbe978ac\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=hk.hkott.app</a><br />\n售價：免費<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唐美鳳<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2019/09/25/icable-news-app-hdr-ott/software/android-app/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2019%2F09%2F25%2Ficable-news-app-hdr-ott%2Fsoftware%2Fandroid-app%2F&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9A1nSF4GOVyTVdrqrZ1TEh8%3D&h=85c882d5\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2019/09/25/icable-news-app-hdr-ott/software/android-app/</a>"},{"pid":"cfd7439ad49cf23012d9c75770b5363e291a12a4","tid":1593694,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"1ffb65913517f6777e0d25d5e2b7c423e2fbdd21","tid":1593694,"uid":1643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T08:25:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有線而家都唔播民間記者會, 走去播支那十一記者會"},{"pid":"8fda2658058f5f312ea39435905d8ce47c1b8be3","tid":1593694,"uid":29751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T10:43:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"479de580af4cbf522911b6909d5450f9c2efe98a","tid":1593694,"uid":71583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9500aa64dd3ed9028bc44c59700e81563ac13969","tid":1593694,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T07:51:02.000Z","msg":"現時很多人都透過智能電話接收新聞資訊，有線寬頻旗下的有線電視亦積極配合市民的習慣轉變，日前宣佈推出全港首個採用 HDR 制式的 24 小時 OTT（over-the-top）直播新聞手機程式「有線新聞 OTT App」，iOS 和 Android 版本已經上架。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/25/141324_92b09e623e988a77340662f23059ac9f.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F25%2F141324_92b09e623e988a77340662f23059ac9f.jpeg&h=ba22bf60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有線新聞 OTT App 提供新聞和財經資訊之餘，亦提供一系列有線新聞製作的節目，還有 24 消息新聞直播，不過此 App 的賣點之一，相信是畫質更佳，更能夠符合用戶要求的 HDR 制式。有線新聞 OTT App 現在屬於試用階段，用戶登記成為會員，可以由即日起至今年 12 月 31 日免費觀看本地、大陸、國際的新聞時事、財經及體育資訊。<br />\n<br />\n正式推出日期預計為明年年初，然後會進一步推出智能電視版本，讓用戶透過手機和智能電視跨平台收看有線新聞直播或點播內容。<br />\n<br />\n有線新聞<br />\n下載：iOS<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%9C%89%E7%B7%9A%E6